Don Bailey (CEO Expand a Sign) presents the cheque to Bateleurs Chairman, Sven Kerher. Founded in 1998, The Bateleurs is a South African non-profit company with over 200 volunteer pilots and aircraft. It provides its beneficiaries and the public with an aerial perspective of the environment and has coordinated several diverse missions throughout South Africa and Africa in support of environmental issues. &#x201c;We are proud to support The Bateleurs and share their dedication and commitment to protecting our environment,&#x201d; says Kirsty Fonzari - Expand a Sign Marketing Manager. For more information visit www.uzwelo.co.za or call Kirsty Fonzari on (031) 207 2327.